@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wtqqct(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((0.37 * (v0 + 0.72 + v1 + 0.98)) - wp.exp(tmp))
    tmp = (0.68 + (wp.sin(tmp + 1.00) * v1))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.77) * 0.41)
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.61) + 0.51)
    v2 = 0.77
    v0 = (wp.abs(v2) / wp.exp((v0 + 0.72 - v0 + 0.39)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.31 - tmp + 0.80) * 0.74))
    data[tid] = v0
